

# Models:

    rails generate model Player id:primary_key name:string surname:string email:string

    rails generate scaffold Player id:primary_key name:string surname:string email:string

    rails generate model Game id:primary_key player_id:integer

# Controllers

    rails generate controller home index

# Mailers

    rails generate mailer PlayerMailer

Migrations

    http://guides.rubyonrails.org/migrations.html

    # standalone migration

    rails generate migration AddPartNumberToProducts part_number:string

    Migration methods:

    add_column
    add_index
    change_column
    change_table
    create_table
    drop_table
    remove_column
    remove_index
    rename_column

    Migrations supported types (will be mapped onto an appropriate underlying database type):

    :binary
    :boolean
    :date
    :datetime
    :decimal
    :float
    :integer
    :primary_key
    :string
    :text
    :time
    :timestamp


